title: Lone Wolf And Cub: 6 White Heaven In Hell

sources.title: Lone Wolf And Cub: 6 White Heaven In Hell
sources.description: In the final  Lone Wolf and Cub  film, star Tomisaburo Wakayama decided to make the sort of wild movie he’d always wanted to: one in which Lone Wolf battles zombies and Daigoro’s baby cart zips improbably across an icy landscape on skis.
